    <p>The aero­space sec­tor fo­cuses on four key ser­vices – man­u­fac­tur­ing; main­te­nance, re­pair op­er­a­tions (MRO); in­no­va­tion; and af­ter­mar­ket ser­vices. It has been hit hard by the fall in de­mand for air travel trig­gered by the Covid-19 pan­demic. 1 per cent of GDP, with</p>
