    <p>to­tal out­put in 2019</p>
    <p>More than</p>
    <p>22,000</p>
    <p>work­ers em­ployed; 80 per cent of the work­ers are lo­cal, and 74 per cent are PMETs.</p>
    <p>Made up of about</p>
    <p>130</p>
    <p>firms</p>
    <p>MRO out­put in Sin­ga­pore alone con­trib­utes to</p>
    <p>10%</p>
    <p>of global out­put</p>
    <p>Key firms op­er­at­ing in Sin­ga­pore in­clude Air­bus, Boe­ing, Bom­bardier, Rolls-Royce and GE Avi­a­tion.</p>
    <p>2,000</p>
